CMD.CHAT.HELP:
Available commands:
[#00FF00]/chat censor[/#] - switching chat censor
[#00FF00]/chat prefix[/#] - switching your chat prefix
[#00FF00]/chat name[/#] - switching your chat name color
[#00FF00]/chat message[/#] - switching your chat message color
[#00FF00]/chat ignore[/#] [#42f4ee]add/remove/list[/#] - managing black list
[#00FF00]/chat sound[/#] [#42f4ee]on/off[/#] - switching private messages sounds
[#00FF00]/chat reset[/#] - set your chat/message color and prefix to default

CMD.CHAT.IGNORE.HELP:
Commands list:
[#00FF00]/chat ignore add[/#] "player name" - add player to your blacklist
[#00FF00]/chat ignore remove[/#] "player name" - remove player from your blacklist
[#00FF00]/chat ignore list[/#] - show your blacklist
